Package tuition

Class TriState

java.lang.Object
tuition.Student
tuition.NonResident
tuition.TriState
public class TriState extends NonResident
This class is derived from NonResident class and contains operations on TriState students. It allows calculation of tuition due for students and also manages origin of student.
Author:
Ria Shah, Christian Bermudez
